{"id": 3066, "genre": 1000, "title": "上网这么久，你觉得自己最适应的线上角色其实是哪种？", "description": "或者说，你觉得自己跟网络的关系最接近哪一种？（题图来自：iStock ©️ ma_rish）", "record_count": 4873, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191121235718MY5cJtnhkOfmTNF0.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-21T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6052, "title": "上网这么久，你觉得自己最适应的线上角色其实是哪种？", "content": "上网这么久，你觉得自己最适应的线上角色其实是哪一种？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349631, "content": "参与者，积极加入公共话题/意见表达/社交互动", "image": "img/option/option/20191121222203quOUIsTAKwL8f49z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349632, "content": "搜索者，线上版信息仓鼠，网络的作用只是资讯来源", "image": "img/option/option/201911212224258AB46DXFQeRvc0St.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349633, "content": "创造者，主要日常是搬运或展示自己的作品/二次创作", "image": "img/option/option/20191121222938fJ7SVFUps01baHPK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349634, "content": "评论者，更喜欢打分/投票/如何评价 xxx 之类的表态", "image": "img/option/option/20191121223147xc3AV5hr8IYZpgNF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349635, "content": "观察者，话不是很多，更喜欢进行线上人类学观察", "image": "img/option/option/20191121224126JgonbPsODw3ZIyFQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349636, "content": "分享者，不生产内容，但积极转发安利各种观点/资源", "image": "img/option/option/20191121225403KsqeHop3rjg97vNt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349637, "content": "谈论者，向外观察相对少一些，主要动力是表达自我", "image": "img/option/option/20191121230146jJ9WwvGicSKQUhq3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349638, "content": "潜行者，做啥基本都自娱自乐，很少真正介入到线上", "image": "img/option/option/20191121232457VjyOaeD0RN8nYgIJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349639, "content": "我也说不清楚/都不是", "image": "img/option/option/20191121231000GzseIDJ8gvoAcV9W.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}